A CIT heist on the R38 between Mbombela and eManzana (formerly Badplaas) necessitated that the road be temporarily closed. The Mpumalanga Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison’s, spokesperson, Moeti Mmusi, has advised motorists to travel between Mbombela and eManzana via alternative roads, such as the R541 through Machadodorp. ALSO READ: Five alleged robbers appear in Graskop Magistrate’s Court after an interprovincial police chase This is a developing story; Lowvelder will keep its readers apprised.